description:
Brooke and Danielle are breaking down some of the BEST gifts to give this holiday season!  The gals include gifts for friends, family, significant others and beyond!  Also, tune in to hear more about the LA trip, some influencer events, and a recap of the gal’s weekends!  Be sure to tag @galsonthegopodcast in your listening selfies/stories on Instagram!
